{"tid":339073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際]John Mccain反對共和黨醫改原因: 反黑箱作業，支持程序公義","createTime":"2017-07-28T17:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T12:56:11.000Z","uid":22054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"978dd688c84b182dbf37e9ad939a90e714a2d33b","tid":339073,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:30:53.000Z","msg":"Washington (CNN)Shortly before Sen. John McCain entered the Senate chamber in the wee hours of Friday morning, reporters wanted to know how he'd vote.<br />\nHe instructed them to &quot;watch the show.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>McCain killed his party's narrowly-crafted Obamacare repeal bill Friday not because he was opposed to dismantling the Affordable Care Act, but because he fundamentally believed the process -- the lack of hearings, the one-party, closed-door negotiations</strong></span>, the fact that in the end all that Republican senators could agree upon was a shell of the plan they'd promised -- was flawed.<br />\nIt was a result that may have been hinted at earlier in the week. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2017/07/28/politics/john-mccain-maverick-health-care/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2Fpolitics%2Fjohn-mccain-maverick-health-care%2Findex.html&d=o1Fh5s5%2FtNpxqMkepdJf%2F7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=edb1dad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2Fpolitics%2Fjohn-mccain-maverick-health-care%2Findex.html&h=9a7bf279\" target=\"_blank\">http://edition.cnn.com/2017/07/28/politics/john-mccain-maverick-health-care/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔理佢咩立場，佢呢個做法真係值得尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji